    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/20ab90148e0765ceebc38466d252e7cd.avif?t=1768150732\" width=800 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你的队员是“回响者”——远程操作的类人生物克隆体，正被派往废弃的空间站和工业遗址执行任务。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你获得的目标：收集有价值的废料、返回列车、粉碎它并提炼珍贵的金属。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请小心，不是只有赤森企业在监视你的每一步…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赤森企业欢迎你，欢迎加入你的第一轮轮班！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/f6299edba5d2c0b9c8893d8bbf6b7cab.poster.avif?t=1768150732\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/f6299edba5d2c0b9c8893d8bbf6b7cab.webm?t=1768150732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/f6299edba5d2c0b9c8893d8bbf6b7cab.mp4?t=1768150732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/986fda7d1989031afa715429a998b3b5.avif?t=1768150732\" width=800 height=66 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择与朋友组队，或独自一人踏入未知的深空废墟。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在黑暗中搜刮战利品，摧毁障碍，换取丰厚奖励 —— 同时拼命求生。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >活下来靠的不只是枪法，更是沟通 —— 是搭救队友，还是转身跑路，由你决定。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包括接近语音聊天 。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/5446c1161b175ce8ca177518ddcc4675.avif?t=1768150732\" width=800 height=66 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>利用环境，在黑暗中潜伏，别发出声音。</strong>声音会吸引……“它们”。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你非常脆弱，任何失誤都可能致命。隐匿、判断与本能，决定你能否活下来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用科技装备 提高你的存活率——但别依赖它们，它们不会一直有效。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次行动都可能是你的最后一步。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入得越深，你就越会意识到：有些东西无法被阻止……</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/19c4202870c95a7490e3e4d51f31fe6c.poster.avif?t=1768150732\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/19c4202870c95a7490e3e4d51f31fe6c.webm?t=1768150732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/319e5aa390c5fdca1c6edb8a8c493b46.avif?t=1768150732\" width=800 height=66 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >空间站基于程序生成算法构建，地图布局变化多端。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次任务都是独一无二的，你无法依赖旧有经验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>它们在进化。</strong>上次奏效的策略，这次可能毫无作用……</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/df403a039d2fa5434219762caa6e92d8.poster.avif?t=1768150732\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/df403a039d2fa5434219762caa6e92d8.webm?t=1768150732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/df403a039d2fa5434219762caa6e92d8.mp4?t=1768150732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/cc6bf3e8c31b05b2a97af3042e4cc6b9.avif?t=1768150732\" width=800 height=66 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >粉碎废料，赚取企业积分，用于升级装备和科技。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强化列车，解锁工具，安装阴险又实用的防御系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >导航设备 帮助你搜刮最有价值的区域，但信息总有代价……</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修理你的列车，否则它可能无法带你回家……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232000/extras/a047032360a330c18b13ee2cc8b366b8.avif?t=1768150732\" width=800 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是回响者。你属于企业。你随时可以被替换。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >履行任务，遵守协议，禁止无谓发问。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轮班开始。列车不会等你——他们也不会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
